*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& Report ZBC400_INTERNAL
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*&
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
REPORT ZBC400_INTERNAL.

DATA: NUMS TYPE I OCCURS 0,
      WA TYPE I.

DO 10 TIMES.

  WA = WA + 1.
  APPEND WA TO NUMS.

  ENDDO.


  LOOP AT NUMS INTO WA.

    WRITE:/ WA.

    ENDLOOP.
